Description: CVE-2026-9547 - libssh: map SSH_KNOWN_HOSTS_OTHER to CURLKHMATCH_MISMATCH
 When libssh reported SSH_KNOWN_HOSTS_OTHER (key type mismatch), curl's
 libssh backend incorrectly fell through to the missing-key path and
 returned CURLKHMATCH_MISSING instead of CURLKHMATCH_MISMATCH.  Because
